<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PDF Upload Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .opportunity-info { background: #e8f4fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .pdf-info { background: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border: 2px solid #28a745; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .highlight { color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; }
        .action-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìÑ New PDF Document Uploaded</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello Administrator,</h2>
            
            <p>A RH user has uploaded a new PDF document for an approved opportunity that requires your review.</p>
            
            <div class="opportunity-info">
                <h3>üìã Opportunity Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{ opportunity.name }}</span></p>
                <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{ opportunity.company }}</p>
                <p><strong>Value:</strong> {{ opportunity.value }} DT</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #28a745; font-weight: 600;">‚úÖ Approved</span></p>
                <p><strong>Deadline:</strong> {{ opportunity.closeDate|date("Y-m-d") }}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pdf-info">
                <h3>üìÑ PDF Document Information:</h3>
                <p><strong>File Name:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{ file.originalFilename }}</span></p>
                <p><strong>File Size:</strong> {{ (file.fileSize / 1024)|round(1) }} KB</p>
                <p><strong>Uploaded By:</strong> {{ uploadedBy.name ?? uploadedBy.email }}</p>
                <p><strong>Upload Date:</strong> {{ uploadDate|date("Y-m-d H:i:s") }}</p>
                
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <a href="{{ app_url }}/admin/download-pdf/{{ file.id }}" class="action-button" target="_blank" style="background: #007bff; margin-right: 10px;">
                        üì• Download PDF
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{ app_url }}/admin/opportunities" class="action-button" target="_blank">
                        üîç View Opportunity
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Please log into the system to review this PDF document and take appropriate action.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <a href="{{ app_url }}/admin/opportunities" class="action-button" target="_blank">
                    üîç Review Opportunity & PDF
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from the HR Management System.</p>
            <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 